Package: RHive
Type: Package
Title: R and Hive
Version: 0.0-6
Description: RHive is an R extension facilitating
			distributed computing via HIVE query.
			It provides an easy to use HQL like SQL 
			and R objects and functions in HQL.
Author: NexR
Maintainer: NexR <rhive@nexr.com>
License: Apache License (== 2.0)
Depends: R (>= 2.13.0), rJava (>= 0.9-0)
Enhances: rJava
SystemRequirements: Hadoop core >= 0.20.3 (http://hadoop.apache.org/core/), 
                    Hive >= 0.8 (http://hive.apache.org/)
Repository: CRAN
